<footer>
	<div class="footer-content">
		<img src="/floodboy-logo.png" alt="Floodboy Logo" />
		<span class="brand">FloodBoy: IoT-Powered Blockchain</span>
		<span class="separator">|</span>
		<span class="tagline">Real-time flood monitoring for smart cities</span>
	</div>
	<div class="footer-info">
		<span class="git-info">Git: <code>21205b5</code> (2025-07-23)</span>
		<span class="separator">â€¢</span>
		<span class="contract-info">Factory (JIBCHAIN): <a href="https://exp.jibchain.net/address/0x904f1CCDb682f0E7b82387190C0EbF9015152BE7" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><code>0x904f...5BE7</code></a></span>
